metadata.name: GLIPLE #1 ANUBEAST!!!
metadata.description:
GLIPLE by Aqmal  
GLIPLE is acronym of Glitch People, I present this work for Glitch art fans.  
1/1 artwork with pfp portrait style. The next drop of GLIPLE pricing will follow my ATH.  
UTILITIES FOR HOLDER  
a. Holder will get 9% cashback after winning the bid.  
b. Holder will get 1% of his/her GLIPLE whenever I got sales on GLIPLE series.  
c. Holder will be involved with GLIPLE series development.

THIS CONTRACT APPLIED AS LONG AS I AM ALIVE AND ABLE TO DO MY RESPONSIBILITIES.  
SINCERELY APPRECIATE YOUR SUPPORT.

BEST REGARDS, AQMAL
